        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI think this might be root of a number of problems for appc working in container.\n\nSee https://nexus.onap.org/content/repositories/snapshots/org/onap/ccsdk/sli/core/dblib-provider/ \nfor example of versions for ccsdk components.\n\nSDNC/OAM and SDNC/NORTHBOUND are still in SDNC and version haven't changed.\n\nWill submit another patch to update appc/pom.xml to latest ccsdk parent.",
